    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdminInterface
    The `AdminInterface` defines the business logic and operations that can be performed by an administrator.
    AdminService
    The `AdminService` class provides the business logic and implementation for administrative operations.
    Booking
     
    BookingNotFoundException
    The `BookingNotFoundException` is a custom exception class that is thrown when a booking with a specified ID cannot be found in the system.
    Constant
     
    Customer
    The Customer class extends the base User class to represent a customer within the system.
    CustomerInterface
    The `CustomerInterface` defines the business operations and logic available to a customer in the FlipFit system.
    CustomerService
    The `CustomerService` class implements the `CustomerInterface` to provide all business logic and operations related to a customer.
    DbConnection
    Utility class for managing database connections to the FlipFitSchema.
    Demo
     
    Demo
     
    EmailAlreadyExistsException
    The `EmailAlreadyExistsException` is a custom exception class thrown when a user registration is attempted with an email address that already exists in the system.
    EmailNotFoundException
    Thrown when an email ID is not found in the system.
    FlipFitAdmin
     
    FlipFitBookingDaoImpl
    The `FlipFitBookingDaoImpl` class provides the data access layer for booking-related operations.
    FlipFitCustomerDaoImpl
    The `FlipFitCustomerDaoImpl` class implements the `FlipFitCustomerDAOInterface` to provide the data access layer for customer and user-related operations.
    FlipFitCustomerDAOInterface
    The `FlipFitCustomerDAOInterface` defines the data access object (DAO) contract for customer-related entities.
    FlipFitGym
    The `FlipFitGym` class represents a gym entity within the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitGymDaoImpl
    The `FlipFitGymDaoImpl` class provides the data access layer for gym-related operations.
    FlipFitGymOwnerDaoImpl
    The `FlipFitGymOwnerDaoImpl` class implements the `FlipFitGymOwnerDaoInterface` to provide the data access layer for gym owner-related operations.
    FlipFitGymOwnerDaoInterface
    The `FlipFitGymOwnerDaoInterface` defines the data access object (DAO) contract for `GymOwner` entities.
    FlipFitSlotDaoImpl
    The `FlipFitSlotDaoImpl` class provides the data access layer for slot-related operations.
    GymFlipFitAdminMenu
    The `GymFlipFitAdminMenu` class provides the command-line interface for the administrator.
    GymFlipFitApplication
    The `GymFlipFitApplication` class is the main entry point for the FlipFit application.
    GymFlipFitCustomerMenu
    The `GymFlipFitCustomerMenu` class provides the command-line interface for customer-specific operations.
    GymFlipFitOwnerMenu
    The `GymFlipFitOwnerMenu` class provides the command-line interface for gym owners.
    GymNotFoundException
    Thrown when a gym with the specified ID is not found.
    GymOwner
    The `GymOwner` class extends the `User` class to represent a gym owner in the FlipFit system.
    GymOwnerInterface
    The `GymOwnerInterface` defines the business logic and operations available to a gym owner.
    GymOwnerNotFoundException
    Thrown when a gym owner with the specified ID is not found in the system.
    GymOwnerService
    The `GymOwnerService` class provides the business logic and implementation for gym owner-specific operations, including managing gyms and slots.
    IncorrectCredentialsException
    Thrown when a user provides incorrect email or password during authentication.
    IncorrectRoleSelectedException
    Thrown when a user selects a role that is not valid or doesn't match their credentials.
    IncorrectSlotDetailsEnteredException
    Thrown when the details provided for a gym slot (e.g., start time, end time) are incorrect or invalid.
    InvalidBookingDetailsException
    Thrown when the details provided for a booking are invalid.
    InvalidBookingIdCustomerException
    Thrown when a customer tries to access a booking with an ID that does not belong to them.
    Payment
    The `Payment` class represents a payment transaction in the FlipFit system.
    RegistrationPendingAtAdmin
    Thrown when a user's registration (e.g., a gym owner) is pending approval from the administrator.
    Role
    The `Role` class represents a user role within the FlipFit system.
    Slot
    The `Slot` class represents a time slot available for booking at a gym.
    SlotAlreadyApprovedException
    Thrown when an administrator attempts to approve a gym slot that has already been approved.
    SlotIntersectException
    Thrown when a new slot is created that overlaps in time with an existing slot in the same gym.
    SlotNotFoundException
    Thrown when a specific gym slot with the given ID cannot be found.
    TransactionIdNotUniqueException
    Thrown when a transaction ID provided for a new transaction already exists in the system.
    User
    The `User` class is a base class representing a generic user in the FlipFit system.
    UserNotFoundException
    Thrown when a user with the specified ID is not found in the system.
    WaitlistedBookingsNotFoundException
    Thrown when no waitlisted bookings are found for a given slot.
